column5: Headed up to Big Canon (Vermillion Bay area) this Friday. Has anyone been on RT 53 North of Eau Claire? Any construction delays to be aware of? Same for 502 on the other side of the border? How was the border this year? Thanks for the knowledge.
I just came back from a trip on Monday. 53 was fine, no construction. I crossed at Grand Portage, it was one of the easiest crossings I have ever had.
packpro, just curious and was wondering if you fish with Dave S. ?
